dct_description_sm: Relief shown by spot heights and shading. Includes four distance rings at 5km intervals from Hobart center. Map of Greater Hobart area showing: roads; railroads; walking, hiking, and biking routes; land use; and facilities Includes legend, "Index to Hobart Suburbs with Postcodes," disclaimer, publisher's note, ackowledgement, and text about road classifications and track class definition. Panel title. Includes on verso colored illustrations with accompanying text, and 3 ancillary maps with accompanying scales, legend, and place index. Map is waterproof.
dct_publisher_sm: Eight Mile Plains, Qld. : Hema Maps, ©2021.
